<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="description" content="">
    <meta name="author" content="">
    <title>Blog</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap Core CSS -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/public/lib/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <!-- Custom CSS -->
    <link href="/top/blog/clean-blog.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <!-- Custom Fonts -->
    <link href="/public/lib/font-awesome/css/font-awesome.min.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
    <!--[if lt IE 9]>
        <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/libs/html5shiv/3.7.0/html5shiv.js"></script>
        <script src="https://oss.maxcdn.com/libs/respond.js/1.4.2/respond.min.js"></script>
    <![endif]-->
</head>

<body>
    <%include ../../../public/header/header %>
    <header class="intro-header" style="background-image: url('/images/img/about-bg.jpg')">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
                    <div class="post-heading">
                        <h1><%= blog[0].title %></h1>
                        <span class="meta">write by <%= blog[0].author %></span> <span class=createtime>on <%= blog[0].createtime.toLocaleString() %></span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <!-- Post Content -->
    <article>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-8 col-lg-offset-2 col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
                    <% if(blog) {%>
                        <div class="content"> <%-"     "+blog[0].contentMark()  %></div>
                    <% } else {%>
                        <p>也许是你点击的时候姿势不对，没有找到文章</p>
                        <p>建议返回上个页面，换个姿势，再来一次</p>
                    <% } %>           
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </article>
    <hr>
    <!-- Footer -->
    <%include ../../../public/footer/footer %>
</body>
<script src="/public/lib/seajs-3.0.0/dist/sea.js"></script>
<script>
    seajs.config({
        alias: {
            "jquery": "/public/lib/jquery/jquery-seajs.js",
            "jq-trans": "/public/lib/jquery/jq-transision-seajs.js",
            "bootstrap": "/public/lib/bootstrap/js/bootstrap-seajs.js",
            "less": "/public/lib/less.js",
            "easing": "/public/lib/jquery/jquery.easing.seajs.js",
            "header":"/public/header/header-main"
        }
    });
    seajs.use("/top/blog/singleblog/singleblog-main");
</script>

</html>
